---
title: Gouda Vibes Burgers with Tomato Onion Jam & Potato Wedges
description: Cheeseburgers are pretty much a perfect food. Beef patty, a slice of cheese, maybe a squeeze of ketchup—that’s all you need for a good one. For a GREAT one, however, it’s best to leave it to the pros (aka our chefs) who settle for nothing less. Here, they’re bringing the good vibes by topping beef patties with nutty gouda. The cheesy patties are then sandwiched between toasty buns along with tomato onion jam and a smoky special sauce. Oh, and did we mention there’s potato wedges (aka oven fries) on the side? Goodbye, just-plain-good burgers!
